snippet.title: Gonzzalezz (Opera Soft) (1989) (Amstrad CPC)
snippet.description:
(See all text for English)
Original plataformas de Opera Soft. En Amstrad goza de un colorido destacable, por lo menos en la primera carga.

Original platform game from Opera. In Amstrad has a remarkable color, at least in the first part.
